16#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_LOC_29_C
17#define RDATA_GENERIC_LOC_29_C
18
19#define RRTYPE_LOC_ATTRIBUTES (0)
20
21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_loc(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 int d1, m1, s1;
25 int d2, m2, s2;
26 unsigned char size;
27 unsigned char hp;
28 unsigned char vp;
29 unsigned char version;
30 bool east = false;
31 bool north = false;
32 long tmp;
33 long m;
34 long cm;
35 long poweroften[8] = { 1, 10, 100, 1000,
36 10000, 100000, 1000000, 10000000 };
37 int man;
38 int exp;
39 char *e;
40 int i;
41 unsigned long latitude;
42 unsigned long longitude;
43 unsigned long altitude;
44
45 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_loc);
46
47 UNUSED(type);
48 UNUSED(rdclass);
49 UNUSED(origin);
50 UNUSED(options);
51
52 /*
53 * Defaults.
54 */
55 m1 = s1 = 0;
56 m2 = s2 = 0;
57 size = 0x12; /* 1.00m */
58 hp = 0x16; /* 10000.00 m */
59 vp = 0x13; /* 10.00 m */
60 version = 0;
61
62 /*
63 * Degrees.
64 */
65 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
66 false));
67 if (token.value.as_ulong > 90U)
68 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
69 d1 = (int)token.value.as_ulong;
70 /*
71 * Minutes.
72 */
73 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
74 false));
75 if (strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "N") == 0)
76 north = true;
77 if (north || strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "S") == 0)
78 goto getlong;
79 m1 = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
80 if (*e != 0)
81 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
82 if (m1 < 0 || m1 > 59)
83 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
84 if (d1 == 90 && m1 != 0)
85 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
86
87 /*
88 * Seconds.
89 */
90 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
91 false));
92 if (strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "N") == 0)
93 north = true;
94 if (north || strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "S") == 0)
95 goto getlong;
96 s1 = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
97 if (*e != 0 && *e != '.')
98 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
99 if (s1 < 0 || s1 > 59)
100 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
101 if (*e == '.') {
102 const char *l;
103 e++;
104 for (i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
105 if (*e == 0)
106 break;
107 if ((tmp = decvalue(*e++)) < 0)
108 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
109 s1 *= 10;
110 s1 += tmp;
111 }
112 for (; i < 3; i++)
113 s1 *= 10;
114 l = e;
115 while (*e != 0) {
116 if (decvalue(*e++) < 0)
117 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
118 }
119 if (*l != '\0' && callbacks != NULL) {
120 const char *file = isc_lex_getsourcename(lexer);
121 unsigned long line = isc_lex_getsourceline(lexer);
122
123 if (file == NULL)
124 file = "UNKNOWN";
125 (*callbacks->warn)(callbacks, "%s: %s:%u: '%s' extra "
126 "precision digits ignored",
127 "dns_rdata_fromtext", file, line,
128 DNS_AS_STR(token));
129 }
130 } else
131 s1 *= 1000;
132 if (d1 == 90 && s1 != 0)
133 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
134
135 /*
136 * Direction.
137 */
138 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
139 false));
140 if (strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "N") == 0)
141 north = true;
142 if (!north && strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "S") != 0)
143 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
144
145 getlong:
146 /*
147 * Degrees.
148 */
149 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
150 false));
151 if (token.value.as_ulong > 180U)
152 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
153 d2 = (int)token.value.as_ulong;
154
155 /*
156 * Minutes.
157 */
158 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
159 false));
160 if (strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "E") == 0)
161 east = true;
162 if (east || strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "W") == 0)
163 goto getalt;
164 m2 = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
165 if (*e != 0)
166 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
167 if (m2 < 0 || m2 > 59)
168 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
169 if (d2 == 180 && m2 != 0)
170 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
171
172 /*
173 * Seconds.
174 */
175 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
176 false));
177 if (strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "E") == 0)
178 east = true;
179 if (east || strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "W") == 0)
180 goto getalt;
181 s2 = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
182 if (*e != 0 && *e != '.')
183 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
184 if (s2 < 0 || s2 > 59)
185 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
186 if (*e == '.') {
187 const char *l;
188 e++;
189 for (i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
190 if (*e == 0)
191 break;
192 if ((tmp = decvalue(*e++)) < 0)
193 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
194 s2 *= 10;
195 s2 += tmp;
196 }
197 for (; i < 3; i++)
198 s2 *= 10;
199 l = e;
200 while (*e != 0) {
201 if (decvalue(*e++) < 0)
202 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
203 }
204 if (*l != '\0' && callbacks != NULL) {
205 const char *file = isc_lex_getsourcename(lexer);
206 unsigned long line = isc_lex_getsourceline(lexer);
207
208 if (file == NULL)
209 file = "UNKNOWN";
210 (*callbacks->warn)(callbacks, "%s: %s:%u: '%s' extra "
211 "precision digits ignored",
212 "dns_rdata_fromtext",
213 file, line, DNS_AS_STR(token));
214 }
215 } else
216 s2 *= 1000;
217 if (d2 == 180 && s2 != 0)
218 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
219
220 /*
221 * Direction.
222 */
223 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
224 false));
225 if (strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "E") == 0)
226 east = true;
227 if (!east && strcasecmp(DNS_AS_STR(token), "W") != 0)
228 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
229
230 getalt:
231 /*
232 * Altitude.
233 */
234 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
235 false));
236 m = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
237 if (*e != 0 && *e != '.' && *e != 'm')
238 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
239 if (m < -100000 || m > 42849672)
240 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
241 cm = 0;
242 if (*e == '.') {
243 e++;
244 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
245 if (*e == 0 || *e == 'm')
246 break;
247 if ((tmp = decvalue(*e++)) < 0)
248 return (DNS_R_SYNTAX);
249 cm *= 10;
250 if (m < 0)
251 cm -= tmp;
252 else
253 cm += tmp;
254 }
255 for (; i < 2; i++)
256 cm *= 10;
257 }
258 if (*e == 'm')
259 e++;
260 if (*e != 0)
261 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
262 if (m == -100000 && cm != 0)
263 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
264 if (m == 42849672 && cm > 95)
265 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
266 /*
267 * Adjust base.
268 */
269 altitude = m + 100000;
270 altitude *= 100;
271 altitude += cm;
272
273 /*
274 * Size: optional.
275 */
276 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
277 true));
278 if (token.type == isc_tokentype_eol ||
279 token.type == isc_tokentype_eof) {
280 isc_lex_ungettoken(lexer, &token);
281 goto encode;
282 }
283 m = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
284 if (*e != 0 && *e != '.' && *e != 'm')
285 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
286 if (m < 0 || m > 90000000)
287 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
288 cm = 0;
289 if (*e == '.') {
290 e++;
291 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
292 if (*e == 0 || *e == 'm')
293 break;
294 if ((tmp = decvalue(*e++)) < 0)
295 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
296 cm *= 10;
297 cm += tmp;
298 }
299 for (; i < 2; i++)
300 cm *= 10;
301 }
302 if (*e == 'm')
303 e++;
304 if (*e != 0)
305 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
306 /*
307 * We don't just multiply out as we will overflow.
308 */
309 if (m > 0) {
310 for (exp = 0; exp < 7; exp++)
311 if (m < poweroften[exp+1])
312 break;
313 man = m / poweroften[exp];
314 exp += 2;
315 } else {
316 if (cm >= 10) {
317 man = cm / 10;
318 exp = 1;
319 } else {
320 man = cm;
321 exp = 0;
322 }
323 }
324 size = (man << 4) + exp;
325
326 /*
327 * Horizontal precision: optional.
328 */
329 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
330 true));
331 if (token.type == isc_tokentype_eol ||
332 token.type == isc_tokentype_eof) {
333 isc_lex_ungettoken(lexer, &token);
334 goto encode;
335 }
336 m = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
337 if (*e != 0 && *e != '.' && *e != 'm')
338 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
339 if (m < 0 || m > 90000000)
340 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
341 cm = 0;
342 if (*e == '.') {
343 e++;
344 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
345 if (*e == 0 || *e == 'm')
346 break;
347 if ((tmp = decvalue(*e++)) < 0)
348 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
349 cm *= 10;
350 cm += tmp;
351 }
352 for (; i < 2; i++)
353 cm *= 10;
354 }
355 if (*e == 'm')
356 e++;
357 if (*e != 0)
358 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
359 /*
360 * We don't just multiply out as we will overflow.
361 */
362 if (m > 0) {
363 for (exp = 0; exp < 7; exp++)
364 if (m < poweroften[exp+1])
365 break;
366 man = m / poweroften[exp];
367 exp += 2;
368 } else if (cm >= 10) {
369 man = cm / 10;
370 exp = 1;
371 } else {
372 man = cm;
373 exp = 0;
374 }
375 hp = (man << 4) + exp;
376
377 /*
378 * Vertical precision: optional.
379 */
380 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
381 true));
382 if (token.type == isc_tokentype_eol ||
383 token.type == isc_tokentype_eof) {
384 isc_lex_ungettoken(lexer, &token);
385 goto encode;
386 }
387 m = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
388 if (*e != 0 && *e != '.' && *e != 'm')
389 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
390 if (m < 0 || m > 90000000)
391 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
392 cm = 0;
393 if (*e == '.') {
394 e++;
395 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
396 if (*e == 0 || *e == 'm')
397 break;
398 if ((tmp = decvalue(*e++)) < 0)
399 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
400 cm *= 10;
401 cm += tmp;
402 }
403 for (; i < 2; i++)
404 cm *= 10;
405 }
406 if (*e == 'm')
407 e++;
408 if (*e != 0)
409 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
410 /*
411 * We don't just multiply out as we will overflow.
412 */
413 if (m > 0) {
414 for (exp = 0; exp < 7; exp++)
415 if (m < poweroften[exp+1])
416 break;
417 man = m / poweroften[exp];
418 exp += 2;
419 } else if (cm >= 10) {
420 man = cm / 10;
421 exp = 1;
422 } else {
423 man = cm;
424 exp = 0;
425 }
426 vp = (man << 4) + exp;
427
428 encode:
429 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &version, 1));
430 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &size, 1));
431 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &hp, 1));
432 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &vp, 1));
433 if (north)
434 latitude = 0x80000000 + ( d1 * 3600 + m1 * 60 ) * 1000 + s1;
435 else
436 latitude = 0x80000000 - ( d1 * 3600 + m1 * 60 ) * 1000 - s1;
437 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(latitude, target));
438
439 if (east)
440 longitude = 0x80000000 + ( d2 * 3600 + m2 * 60 ) * 1000 + s2;
441 else
442 longitude = 0x80000000 - ( d2 * 3600 + m2 * 60 ) * 1000 - s2;
443 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(longitude, target));
444
445 return (uint32_tobuffer(altitude, target));
446}

448static inline isc_result_t
449totext_loc(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
450 int d1, m1, s1, fs1;
451 int d2, m2, s2, fs2;
452 unsigned long latitude;
453 unsigned long longitude;
454 unsigned long altitude;
455 bool north;
456 bool east;
457 bool below;
458 isc_region_t sr;
459 char sbuf[sizeof("90000000m")];
460 char hbuf[sizeof("90000000m")];
461 char vbuf[sizeof("90000000m")];
462 /* "89 59 59.999 N 179 59 59.999 E " */
463 /* "-42849672.95m 90000000m 90000000m 90000000m"; */
464 char buf[8*6 + 12*1 + 2*10 + sizeof(sbuf)+sizeof(hbuf)+sizeof(vbuf)];
465 unsigned char size, hp, vp;
466 unsigned long poweroften[8] = { 1, 10, 100, 1000,
467 10000, 100000, 1000000, 10000000 };
468
469 UNUSED(tctx);
470
471 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_loc);
472 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
473
474 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
475
476 if (sr.base[0] != 0)
477 return (ISC_R_NOTIMPLEMENTED);
478
479 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 16);
480
481 size = sr.base[1];
482 INSIST((size&0x0f) < 10 && (size>>4) < 10);
483 if ((size&0x0f)> 1) {
484 snprintf(sbuf, sizeof(sbuf),
485 "%lum", (size>>4) * poweroften[(size&0x0f)-2]);
486 } else {
487 snprintf(sbuf, sizeof(sbuf),
488 "0.%02lum", (size>>4) * poweroften[(size&0x0f)]);
489 }
490 hp = sr.base[2];
491 INSIST((hp&0x0f) < 10 && (hp>>4) < 10);
492 if ((hp&0x0f)> 1) {
493 snprintf(hbuf, sizeof(hbuf),
494 "%lum", (hp>>4) * poweroften[(hp&0x0f)-2]);
495 } else {
496 snprintf(hbuf, sizeof(hbuf),
497 "0.%02lum", (hp>>4) * poweroften[(hp&0x0f)]);
498 }
499 vp = sr.base[3];
500 INSIST((vp&0x0f) < 10 && (vp>>4) < 10);
501 if ((vp&0x0f)> 1) {
502 snprintf(vbuf, sizeof(vbuf),
503 "%lum", (vp>>4) * poweroften[(vp&0x0f)-2]);
504 } else {
505 snprintf(vbuf, sizeof(vbuf),
506 "0.%02lum", (vp>>4) * poweroften[(vp&0x0f)]);
507 }
508 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
509
510 latitude = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
511 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
512 if (latitude >= 0x80000000) {
513 north = true;
514 latitude -= 0x80000000;
515 } else {
516 north = false;
517 latitude = 0x80000000 - latitude;
518 }
519 fs1 = (int)(latitude % 1000);
520 latitude /= 1000;
521 s1 = (int)(latitude % 60);
522 latitude /= 60;
523 m1 = (int)(latitude % 60);
524 latitude /= 60;
525 d1 = (int)latitude;
526 INSIST(latitude <= 90U);
527
528 longitude = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
529 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
530 if (longitude >= 0x80000000) {
531 east = true;
532 longitude -= 0x80000000;
533 } else {
534 east = false;
535 longitude = 0x80000000 - longitude;
536 }
537 fs2 = (int)(longitude % 1000);
538 longitude /= 1000;
539 s2 = (int)(longitude % 60);
540 longitude /= 60;
541 m2 = (int)(longitude % 60);
542 longitude /= 60;
543 d2 = (int)longitude;
544 INSIST(longitude <= 180U);
545
546 altitude = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
547 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
548 if (altitude < 10000000U) {
549 below = true;
550 altitude = 10000000 - altitude;
551 } else {
552 below =false;
553 altitude -= 10000000;
554 }
555
556 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf),
557 "%d %d %d.%03d %s %d %d %d.%03d %s %s%lu.%02lum %s %s %s",
558 d1, m1, s1, fs1, north ? "N" : "S",
559 d2, m2, s2, fs2, east ? "E" : "W",
560 below ? "-" : "", altitude/100, altitude % 100,
561 sbuf, hbuf, vbuf);
562
563 return (str_totext(buf, target));
564}

566static inline isc_result_t
567fromwire_loc(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
568 isc_region_t sr;
569 unsigned char c;
570 unsigned long latitude;
571 unsigned long longitude;
572
573 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_loc);
574
575 UNUSED(type);
576 UNUSED(rdclass);
577 UNUSED(dctx);
578 UNUSED(options);
579
580 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
581 if (sr.length < 1)
582 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
583 if (sr.base[0] != 0) {
584 /* Treat as unknown. */
585 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
586 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
587 }
588 if (sr.length < 16)
589 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
590
591 /*
592 * Size.
593 */
594 c = sr.base[1];
595 if (c != 0)
596 if ((c&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) == 0)
597 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
598
599 /*
600 * Horizontal precision.
601 */
602 c = sr.base[2];
603 if (c != 0)
604 if ((c&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) == 0)
605 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
606
607 /*
608 * Vertical precision.
609 */
610 c = sr.base[3];
611 if (c != 0)
612 if ((c&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) == 0)
613 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
614 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
615
616 /*
617 * Latitude.
618 */
619 latitude = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
620 if (latitude < (0x80000000UL - 90 * 3600000) ||
621 latitude > (0x80000000UL + 90 * 3600000))
622 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
623 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
624
625 /*
626 * Longitude.
627 */
628 longitude = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
629 if (longitude < (0x80000000UL - 180 * 3600000) ||
630 longitude > (0x80000000UL + 180 * 3600000))
631 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
632
633 /*
634 * Altitude.
635 * All values possible.
636 */
637
638 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
639 isc_buffer_forward(source, 16);
640 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 16));
641}

643static inline isc_result_t
644towire_loc(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
645 UNUSED(cctx);
646
647 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_loc);
648 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
649
650 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
651}
652
653static inline int
654compare_loc(ARGS_COMPARE) {
655 isc_region_t r1;
656 isc_region_t r2;
657
658 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
659 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
660 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_loc);
661 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
662 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
663
664 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
665 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
666 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
667}
668
669static inline isc_result_t
670fromstruct_loc(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
671 dns_rdata_loc_t *loc = source;
672 uint8_t c;
673
674 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_loc);
675 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
676 REQUIRE(loc->common.rdtype == type);
677 REQUIRE(loc->common.rdclass == rdclass);
678
679 UNUSED(type);
680 UNUSED(rdclass);
681
682 if (loc->v.v0.version != 0)
683 return (ISC_R_NOTIMPLEMENTED);
684 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(loc->v.v0.version, target));
685
686 c = loc->v.v0.size;
687 if ((c&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) == 0)
688 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
689 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(loc->v.v0.size, target));
690
691 c = loc->v.v0.horizontal;
692 if ((c&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) == 0)
693 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
694 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(loc->v.v0.horizontal, target));
695
696 c = loc->v.v0.vertical;
697 if ((c&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) > 9 || ((c>>4)&0xf) == 0)
698 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
699 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(loc->v.v0.vertical, target));
700
701 if (loc->v.v0.latitude < (0x80000000UL - 90 * 3600000) ||
702 loc->v.v0.latitude > (0x80000000UL + 90 * 3600000))
703 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
704 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(loc->v.v0.latitude, target));
705
706 if (loc->v.v0.longitude < (0x80000000UL - 180 * 3600000) ||
707 loc->v.v0.longitude > (0x80000000UL + 180 * 3600000))
708 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
709 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(loc->v.v0.longitude, target));
710 return (uint32_tobuffer(loc->v.v0.altitude, target));
711}
712
713static inline isc_result_t
714tostruct_loc(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
715 dns_rdata_loc_t *loc = target;
716 isc_region_t r;
717 uint8_t version;
718
719 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_loc);
720 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
721 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
722
723 UNUSED(mctx);
724
725 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
726 version = uint8_fromregion(&r);
727 if (version != 0)
728 return (ISC_R_NOTIMPLEMENTED);
729
730 loc->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
731 loc->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
732 ISC_LINK_INIT(&loc->common, link);
733
734 loc->v.v0.version = version;
735 isc_region_consume(&r, 1);
736 loc->v.v0.size = uint8_fromregion(&r);
737 isc_region_consume(&r, 1);
738 loc->v.v0.horizontal = uint8_fromregion(&r);
739 isc_region_consume(&r, 1);
740 loc->v.v0.vertical = uint8_fromregion(&r);
741 isc_region_consume(&r, 1);
742 loc->v.v0.latitude = uint32_fromregion(&r);
743 isc_region_consume(&r, 4);
744 loc->v.v0.longitude = uint32_fromregion(&r);
745 isc_region_consume(&r, 4);
746 loc->v.v0.altitude = uint32_fromregion(&r);
747 isc_region_consume(&r, 4);
748 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
749}

753 dns_rdata_loc_t *loc = source;
754
755 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
756 REQUIRE(loc->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_loc);
757
758 UNUSED(source);
759 UNUSED(loc);
760}

779 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
780
